race.description: Book At Gatton Jubilee Golf Club 5462 1420 Handicap
race.comment: APOLLO TEN (1) finished fourth over 1000m at Sunshine Coast at his most recent appearance on July 13. Has ability and should be right in the finish. MILESTONE (7) was out of the money when resuming from a spell last start over 1000m at Gold Coast, beaten 2 lengths after being in contention on the turn. Finds a suitable assignment and can get the job done. FANCI FLEUR (10) had been in top form with two wins on end prior to a third last time out at this track. Coming back in journey today and rates a genuine top-three contender on best form. BONNIE AMORE (3) didn't fire a shot first-up for the new stable when sent out favourite. Was almost too bad to be true. Willing to give another chance.
